202
00:08:32,849 --> 00:08:35,060
I of course don’t approve of that kind of
behavior.

203
00:08:35,060 --> 00:08:37,479
So I can definitely appreciate where you’re
coming from.

204
00:08:37,479 --> 00:08:39,800
However, the problem is China Uncensored

205
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:42,469
is already being squeezed by YouTube.

206
00:08:42,469 --> 00:08:44,399
And Patreon is still the best way for us

207
00:08:44,399 --> 00:08:45,910
to raise funds for the show.

208
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:48,670
I started to look into Patreon alternatives,

209
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:50,320
like SubscribeStar,

210
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,320
but guess what?

211
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:54,550
It doesn’t always go well for alternatives.

212
00:08:54,550 --> 00:08:57,070
And even though SubscribeStar is starting
to resume payments,

213
00:08:57,070 --> 00:08:59,550
it’s too big a risk for us.

214
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:02,120
We are working on creating our own alternative,

215
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,720
but to do that, we still need funding.

216
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:08,670
And right now, Patreon is the best option
for us.

217
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:12,070
You can visit our website to make a direct
PayPal contribution,

218
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:14,959
but we don’t have a good way of making sure
you get rewards—

219
00:09:14,959 --> 00:09:17,690
like me answering your questions on the show
like this.

220
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:19,000
So we prefer Patreon.

221
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:22,370
I know many of you have expressed you’re
not a fan of Patreon,

222
00:09:22,370 --> 00:09:25,410
but for now, I’d ask you to hold out just
a bit longer

223
00:09:25,410 --> 00:09:27,540
for the sake of China Uncensored.

224
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:28,540
If you ditch Patreon,

225
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:30,589
it doesn’t hurt Patreon much,

226
00:09:30,589 --> 00:09:33,940
but it hurts China Uncensored a lot.

227
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:37,420
Thanks for you question and thanks for your
support.

228
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,660
And to all you thanks for watching.

229
